PrecisAmendments to the UNEMPLOYMENT INSURANCE REGULATIONS respecting the manner in which the number of weeks of insurable employment is to be determined in cases where the "pay period" is something other than a calendar week as currently defined in the Regulations (i.e. Sunday to Saturday).

precis:
Amendments to the UNEMPLOYMENT INSURANCE REGULATIONS respecting the manner
in which the number of weeks of insurable employment is to be determined in
cases where the "pay period" is something other than a calendar week as
currently defined in the Regulations (i.e. Sunday to Saturday).
